reviews.reviewTitle: Makes a huge difference for winter driving
reviews.reviewText: It seriously insulates. I suppose it depends on what your steering wheel is made of but I find the steering wheel in my new (used) vehicle to be brutally frigid. This cover improved on that hugely and it actually feels more comfortable to grip. The bit of bling doesn’t hurt either.It doesn’t slide right on but I didn’t find it as difficult to install as others.
Love how it looks. Easy to put on. Don’t know about drying power as it hasn’t gotten wet. I’ve had it for a short time so can’t comment on durability or how well the decorations will stay on.
Nice tight fit and looks great
